00:41.875 --> 00:44.145
- OH, LET ME SEE.
LET ME SEE, HARRY.

00:44.178 --> 00:46.114
HARRY, GET OFF.

00:46.147 --> 00:49.083
[camera snapping pictures]
WHAT'S HE DOING?

00:49.117 --> 00:51.085
