WITH DR. DEBBIE SHIELDS.

01:26.754 --> 01:28.322
- LOOKS LIKE THEY'RE
GIRLFRIENDS.

01:28.356 --> 01:29.823
- DEBBIE, THE BLOND,
WAS BEING RAPED

01:29.857 --> 01:32.726
WHEN ANN, HER DOMESTIC PARTNER,
CAME HOME.

01:32.760 --> 01:36.830
