ON YOUR NEIGHBORS?

01:51.879 --> 01:53.214
- THE CURTAINS
WERE WIDE OPEN.

01:53.247 --> 01:54.315
- AND HE TOOK IT
AS AN INVITATION

01:54.348 --> 01:55.149
TO TAKE SOME PICTURES.

01:55.183 --> 01:57.651
