STARING AT ME.

07:41.662 --> 07:45.065
- DID HE SAY ANYTHING?

07:45.098 --> 07:49.670
- JUST THAT HE WOULD CURE ME
OF FALMOUTH.

07:49.703 --> 07:51.972
