24:54.661 --> 24:55.895
WELCOME TO THE HOUSE, ELLIOT.

24:55.928 --> 24:59.599
- THANK YOU.
IT'S NICE MEETING YOU, COURTNEY.

25:03.870 --> 25:05.572
- ARE YOU A COP?

25:05.605 --> 25:08.107
- EXCUSE ME?

25:08.140 --> 25:09.809
- I'VE SCREWED, LIKE,
WHOLE PRECINCTS.

25:09.842 --> 25:12.545
COPS CAN BE SEX ADDICTS.
IT'S OKAY.

25:12.579 --> 25:14.581
- [chuckles]

25:14.614 --> 25:16.115
SORRY.
I'M AN ACCOUNTANT.

25:16.148 --> 25:17.684
- OH.

25:17.717 --> 25:19.218
YOU COME OFF DIFFERENTLY.

25:19.251 --> 25:20.920
- OKAY, GUYS.

25:20.953 --> 25:22.555
BEDTIME.

25:22.589 --> 25:25.224
GOOD NIGHT.

25:25.257 --> 25:29.128
- GOOD NIGHT.

25:29.161 --> 25:31.964
- OH, HEY, ELLIOT.

25:31.998 --> 25:33.933
HOW'S DAY ONE
OF YOUR NEW LIFE?

25:33.966 --> 25:36.969
- INTERESTING.
THAT'S FOR SURE.

25:37.003 --> 25:38.871
- OH, UM, BY THE WAY,
YOU, UM--

25:38.905 --> 25:43.843
YOU CAN'T--
CAN'T WEAR THAT TOO SLEEP.

25:43.876 --> 25:45.645
- MODESTY RULE?
EVEN FOR BED?

25:45.678 --> 25:49.081
- ESPECIALLY FOR BED.
[chuckles]

25:52.084 --> 25:53.085
HERE.
STANDARD ISSUE.

25:53.119 --> 25:56.889
- THANKS.
HOW'D YOU GET THE CUT?

25:56.923 --> 26:00.960
- WELL, HOW'D I GET
ANY OF 'EM?

26:00.993 --> 26:04.797
ACTUALLY, IT'S PART
OF MY ADDICTION.

26:04.831 --> 26:07.667
I USED TO HIRE PROSTITUTES
TO CUT ME.

26:07.700 --> 26:10.837
THIS ONE'S ACTUALLY
ALL HEALED UP.

26:10.870 --> 26:14.674
- JUST KEEP IT BANDAGED
TO REMIND ME.

26:14.707 --> 26:16.643
- SO STABLER'S UNDERCOVER
IN JACKSON'S CLINIC?

26:16.676 --> 26:18.310
- HE'S WORKING AS FAST
AS HE CAN WHILE JACKSON'S

26:18.344 --> 26:20.112
AT ANN'S BEDSIDE.

26:20.146 --> 26:21.280
- FIND ANYONE
AT THE OTHER REHABS

26:21.313 --> 26:22.949
WHO COULD BE OUR PERP?

26:22.982 --> 26:24.851
- WE LOOKED INTO EMPLOYMENT
RECORDS AT UTICA,

26:24.884 --> 26:26.318
PHILLY, RICHMOND.

26:26.352 --> 26:28.020
SHRINKS, JANITORS, VENDORS.

26:28.054 --> 26:29.155
WE CAME UP EMPTY.

26:29.188 --> 26:31.991
- SO HE'S DEFINITELY A PATIENT,
PROTECTED BY PRIVILEGE.

26:32.024 --> 26:34.160
- ELLIOT'S OUR BEST BET
TO FIND THIS GUY.

26:34.193 --> 26:37.096
SPEAKING OF WHICH,
HE SHOULD BE CALLING ANY MINUTE.

26:37.129 --> 26:38.898
- ARE PHONES ALLOWED IN REHAB?

26:38.931 --> 26:41.133
- NO, THE PATIENTS WERE CAUGHT
SECRETLY SEXTING EACH OTHER.

26:41.167 --> 26:43.135
ELLIOT SNUCK HIS IN.

26:43.169 --> 26:44.971
- I DON'T WANT TO KNOW HOW.

26:45.004 --> 26:48.107
- ELLIOT, HOW'S IT GOING?

26:48.140 --> 26:50.342
- SLOWER THAN I THOUGHT.

26:50.376 --> 26:53.079
GOT MYSELF ON BROOM DUTY SO
I CAN POKE AROUND A LITTLE BIT.

26:53.112 --> 26:55.281
- SEE ANYONE
WITH A CUT FOREARM?

26:55.314 --> 26:56.816
- NO, NOT YET,
BUT THE NEXT STOP

26:56.849 --> 26:58.050
IS THE LAUNDRY ROOM.

26:58.084 --> 27:00.086
MAYBE SOMEONE WASHED HIS SHIRT
TRYING TO GET THE BLOOD OUT.

27:00.119 --> 27:01.654
- WHAT DOES YOUR GUT SAY?

27:01.688 --> 27:03.823
- OH, YOU KNOW,
WHERE DO I START?

27:03.856 --> 27:07.059
WE GOT A GUY NAMED CLAY,
WHO ENJOYS RAPING 16--

27:09.829 --> 27:11.664
- HAVE YOU BEEN A NAUGHTY BOY,
ELLIOT?

27:11.698 --> 27:12.965
- WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

27:12.999 --> 27:14.667
- GOOD MORNING.

27:14.701 --> 27:16.235
WHERE'S DR. JACKSON?

27:16.268 --> 27:18.037
- OH, YOU JUST MISSED HIM.

27:18.070 --> 27:19.706
CAP LOOKED EXHAUSTED
AND SO I TOLD HIM

27:19.739 --> 27:21.007
TO GO GET SOME SLEEP.

27:21.040 --> 27:22.208
- HE WENT HOME?

27:22.241 --> 27:24.677
'CAUSE I NEEDED
TO ASK HIM A QUESTION.

27:24.711 --> 27:25.978
- UH, HE WENT TO HIS CLINIC.

27:26.012 --> 27:27.714
HE SAID SEX ADDICTS
ARE A DELICATE BUNCH

27:27.747 --> 27:29.048
AND HE NEEDED TO CHECK IN.

27:29.081 --> 27:31.417
- GREAT.
THANKS.

27:31.450 --> 27:33.953
- YOU WERE ON THE PHONE.

27:33.986 --> 27:36.122
- NO, I WASN'T.
PHONES AREN'T ALLOWED.

27:36.155 --> 27:38.024
[cell phone vibrates]

27:38.057 --> 27:40.392
- I KNEW IT.

27:40.426 --> 27:45.798
OH, THOSE ARE COP REFLEXES.

27:45.832 --> 27:47.967
DID YOU THINK I WAS GRABBING
FOR YOUR GUN?

27:48.000 --> 27:49.969
LET ME GO OR I'LL SCREAM.

27:50.002 --> 27:52.038
- OKAY, RELAX.

27:56.743 --> 27:58.711
- OLIVIA.

27:58.745 --> 28:01.948
SHE YOUR GIRLFRIEND?

28:01.981 --> 28:03.950
- WHAT'S IT TO YOU?

28:03.983 --> 28:05.351
- THE THREE OF US
COULD HAVE SOME FUN.

28:05.384 --> 28:06.886
- NO, I NEED THAT BACK.

28:06.919 --> 28:07.954
COURTNEY.
- YEAH?

28:07.987 --> 28:09.455
- DON'T DO THAT.

28:09.488 --> 28:10.723
COURTNEY, DON'T DO THAT.

28:10.757 --> 28:13.826
- COME AND GET IT.

28:17.029 --> 28:18.497
- COURTNEY, DON'T DO THAT.

28:18.530 --> 28:20.132
PUT YOUR SHIRT BACK ON.

28:20.166 --> 28:23.369
- DOES OLIVIA PUT OUT, HONEY?

28:23.402 --> 28:25.037
DOES SHE SATISFY YOU?

28:25.071 --> 28:26.105
- DON'T.
DON'T.

28:26.138 --> 28:27.173
THIS IS NOT GOOD FOR YOU.

28:27.206 --> 28:28.741
DON'T DO THIS.

28:28.775 --> 28:30.810
- BUT IT'S SO GOOD FOR YOU.

28:30.843 --> 28:33.445
- STOP.

28:33.479 --> 28:35.114
COURTNEY, THERE'S NO NEED
FOR THIS.

28:35.147 --> 28:36.816
- YOU GAY OR SOMETHING?

28:36.849 --> 28:37.984
- COURTNEY, LISTEN TO ME.

28:38.017 --> 28:39.518
MY DAUGHTER HAD TROUBLE
WITH DRUGS.

28:39.551 --> 28:41.053
SHE WAS PROMISCUOUS,
BUT SHE'S CLEAN.

28:41.087 --> 28:42.955
YOU'RE CLEAN.

28:42.989 --> 28:44.891
YOU'RE CLEAN.

28:44.924 --> 28:46.225
- YOU'RE A WALKING DOUCHEBAG.

28:46.258 --> 28:48.127
WON'T SCREW A PERFECTLY
GOOD PIECE OF TAIL.

28:48.160 --> 28:50.096
- JUST GIVE ME MY PHONE.

28:50.129 --> 28:51.998
- SOMEONE'S COMING.
FOLD SOMETHING.

28:52.031 --> 28:53.065
- GIVE ME THE PHONE, PLEASE.

28:53.099 --> 28:56.468
- NO!

28:56.502 --> 29:00.072
[door opens]

29:00.106 --> 29:01.107
- WHAT ARE YOU GUYS DOING?

29:01.140 --> 29:02.975
- LEAVING.

29:03.009 --> 29:04.043
- I'M DOING MY LAUNDRY.

29:04.076 --> 29:07.113
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

29:07.146 --> 29:10.149
- I'M JUST LOOKING FOR A SHIRT.

29:10.182 --> 29:12.218
GROUP'S MEETING EARLY TODAY.

29:12.251 --> 29:16.522
STARTS NOW.

29:16.555 --> 29:18.757
[door closes]

29:24.096 --> 29:26.565
- HEY, WHAT KIND OF SHIRT
WERE YOU LOOKING FOR?

29:26.598 --> 29:28.067
MAYBE I SAW IT.

29:28.100 --> 29:30.502
- LAUNDRY, MY ASS.

29:30.536 --> 29:32.571
YOU WERE GONNA
DO GANG-BANG GIRL.

29:32.604 --> 29:35.341
HER MOUTH WILL TAKE YOU
TO NIRVANA, MAN.

29:35.374 --> 29:36.976
SO I'M TOLD.

29:37.009 --> 29:39.045
- NIRVANA, HUH?

29:39.078 --> 29:41.447
HUH.
- GOOD MORNING.

29:41.480 --> 29:43.482
[class responds with greetings]

29:55.327 --> 29:58.030
- DR. JACKSON,
MY NAME IS ELLIOT,

29:58.064 --> 30:03.002
AND YOUR BOOK...
CHANGED MY LIFE.

30:03.035 --> 30:05.337
YOUR COURAGE...

30:05.371 --> 30:10.076
YOUR DO-THE-RIGHT-THING
MORAL CODE.

30:10.109 --> 30:14.280
YOU ARE THE REASON
WHY I'M HERE.

30:18.017 --> 30:20.419
- WELCOME, ELLIOT.
I'M GLAD YOU'RE HERE.

30:20.452 --> 30:22.454
[applause]

30:35.034 --> 30:36.335
- THANK YOU,
DR. KINCAID.

30:36.368 --> 30:38.370
- ELLIOT?

30:42.541 --> 30:44.944
HOW DARE YOU COME HERE
UNDER FALSE PRETENSES.

30:44.977 --> 30:46.545
- HOW DARE YOU PROTECT
A SERIAL RAPIST.

30:46.578 --> 30:49.315
- YOU ARE JEOPARDIZING EVERY--
- THANKS, DOC.

30:49.348 --> 30:51.050
- EVERYTHING I DO
TO HELP THESE PATIENTS.

30:51.083 --> 30:52.251
- YEAH.
REALLY?

30:52.284 --> 30:54.520
LIKE CLAY GIBSON?

30:54.553 --> 30:56.422
I MEAN, HE IS THE GOD-OF-LOVE
RAPIST, ISN'T HE?

30:56.455 --> 30:59.025
- I DON'T KNOW IF IT'S HIM.

30:59.058 --> 31:01.427
- WELL, IS THAT THE ONLY GROUP
THAT YOU MENTIONED FALMOUTH TO?

31:01.460 --> 31:03.362
IS IT?

31:03.395 --> 31:04.496
SO YOU CALL ANOTHER MEETING

31:04.530 --> 31:06.632
AND YOU GET WHOEVER IT IS

31:06.665 --> 31:09.368
TO ADMIT TO WHAT HE'S DONE.

31:09.401 --> 31:12.104
- THERE'S NOTHING
I WOULD LIKE MORE

31:12.138 --> 31:13.372
FOR HIS OWN REDEMPTION,

31:13.405 --> 31:15.074
BUT NOT WITH YOU HERE.

31:15.107 --> 31:16.442
- YOU DON'T WANT REDEMPTION
FOR HIM.

31:16.475 --> 31:18.477
YOU WANT IT FOR YOURSELF.

31:18.510 --> 31:21.413
IN THE MEANTIME,
MORE WOMEN GET RAPED.

31:21.447 --> 31:24.383
NOW, MAYBE YOU CAN
LET THAT HAPPEN,

31:24.416 --> 31:29.956
BUT I CAN'T.

31:29.989 --> 31:33.325
CLAY GIBSON, 35, TWO MISDEMEANOR
ASSAULTS, BAR FIGHTS.

31:33.359 --> 31:35.261
HIS DNA'S NOT ON FILE,
BUT TEN-TO-ONE

31:35.294 --> 31:38.164
IT MATCHES THE BLOOD
ON HOLLY'S KNIFE.

31:38.197 --> 31:39.966
- SO THIS GUY WAS RAPING
16-YEAR-OLDS

31:39.999 --> 31:41.567
AND HE'S NOWHERE ON OUR RADAR?

31:41.600 --> 31:43.669
- MAKES YOU WONDER
HOW MANY MORE ARE OUT THERE.

31:43.702 --> 31:45.037
- WELL, I JUST SPENT
A LOVELY EVENING

31:45.071 --> 31:46.305
WITH ABOUT A DOZEN OF THEM.

31:46.338 --> 31:48.140
THIS HAS GOT TO BE OUR GUY.

31:48.174 --> 31:49.541
HE USED THE WORD "NIRVANA."

31:49.575 --> 31:52.444
YOU KNOW, THE REALM
OF THE INDIAN GODS.

31:52.478 --> 31:55.147
- BUT IF WE'RE WRONG,
ANOTHER WOMAN GETS RAPED

31:55.181 --> 31:57.716
AND THE REAL PERP SLIPS TOWN.

31:57.749 --> 31:59.418
DO BACKGROUND ON EVERY PATIENT.

31:59.451 --> 32:01.553
- I DON'T HAVE
THEIR LAST NAMES.

32:01.587 --> 32:04.256
BUT HE DOES.

32:04.290 --> 32:06.492
- ELLIOT--
EXCUSE ME.

32:06.525 --> 32:08.995
YOU WERE RIGHT.

32:09.028 --> 32:10.262
BUT YOU SEE,
I COULDN'T CONDEMN HIM

32:10.296 --> 32:12.999
WITHOUT CONDEMNING MYSELF.

32:13.032 --> 32:16.268
AND EVERYTHING I'VE DONE
HAS BEEN AN ATTEMPT

32:16.302 --> 32:20.739
TO RUN AWAY FROM MY OWN CRIME.

32:20.772 --> 32:22.441
- TIME TO STOP RUNNING.

32:22.474 --> 32:24.476
- YEAH.

32:28.380 --> 32:30.416
- DR. JACKSON.

32:30.449 --> 32:33.485
BEEN A LONG TIME.

32:33.519 --> 32:38.257
- YOU'RE...ANN'S OLD FRIEND?

32:38.290 --> 32:41.093
LINDA.

32:41.127 --> 32:43.029
- DR. JACKSON HERE
HAS BEEN TELLING US

32:43.062 --> 32:45.497
ABOUT A CERTAIN NIGHT
ON THE DOCK IN FALMOUTH

32:45.531 --> 32:48.034
20 YEARS AGO.

32:48.067 --> 32:51.737
SOMETHING HAPPENED AND ANN
STOPPED SPEAKING TO HIM.

32:51.770 --> 32:53.572
- ANN TELL YOU ABOUT THAT?

32:53.605 --> 32:54.740
- NO.

32:54.773 --> 32:56.442
UM, BUT I WAS THERE.

32:56.475 --> 32:58.577
- OKAY.

32:58.610 --> 33:00.446
CAN YOU TELL US WHAT HAPPENED?

33:00.479 --> 33:04.050
- ANN AND I WERE
SKINNY-DIPPING

33:04.083 --> 33:08.187
AND YOU CAME DOWN.

33:08.220 --> 33:10.456
- GO ON.

33:10.489 --> 33:12.458
I NEED TO HEAR THIS.

33:12.491 --> 33:13.425
- HE DOESN'T REMEMBER.

33:13.459 --> 33:16.462
- OH, WELL, YOU WERE DRUNK.

33:16.495 --> 33:19.665
SO, UM...

33:19.698 --> 33:22.134
YOU STRIPPED AND JUMPED IN.

33:22.168 --> 33:24.703
- STRIPPED NAKED?
- YES.

33:24.736 --> 33:27.473
ANN GOT UPSET AND...

33:27.506 --> 33:31.577
SHE WENT BACK UP
TO THE HOUSE.

33:31.610 --> 33:32.678
- ANN LEFT?

33:32.711 --> 33:35.114
- YES, BUT I STAYED

33:35.147 --> 33:37.683
AND...
YOU CAME AFTER ME

33:37.716 --> 33:40.319
AND THERE WAS
NO STOPPING YOU AND--

33:40.352 --> 33:42.654
- DID I--

33:42.688 --> 33:44.723
- YEAH, WE HAD SEX ON THE DOCK.

33:44.756 --> 33:46.492
- HOLD ON.

33:46.525 --> 33:47.826
YOU AND JACKSON?

33:47.859 --> 33:49.595
NOT ANN?
- ANN?

33:49.628 --> 33:52.498
OH, NO!
NO.

33:52.531 --> 33:55.334
IT WAS CAP AND ME.

33:55.367 --> 33:59.205
NO, IT WAS--

34:04.243 --> 34:06.345
- LINDA, I AM SO SORRY.

34:06.378 --> 34:07.546
- OH, NO.
DON'T BE.

34:07.579 --> 34:12.718
I MEAN, THAT WAS--THAT WAS
A CRAZY SUMMER FOR ME SEXUALLY.

34:12.751 --> 34:14.420
I WANTED TO DO IT.

34:14.453 --> 34:20.392
I WAS 17
AND I DON'T REGRET IT.

34:20.426 --> 34:24.463
- WHY DID ANN STOP TALKING
TO ME?

34:24.496 --> 34:28.634
- OH, I WAS ANN'S FIRST LOVE.

34:28.667 --> 34:31.270
WE BROKE HER HEART THAT NIGHT.

34:31.303 --> 34:33.505
- [deep exhale]

34:33.539 --> 34:36.675
- OH, GOD,
SHE BLAMED IT ALL ON YOU.

34:36.708 --> 34:39.711
I'M SO SORRY, CAP.

34:45.451 --> 34:47.419
- LET'S GO AND FIND HIM.

34:47.453 --> 34:53.292
LET'S GO AND FIND THAT MAN
THAT ATTACKED MY DAUGHTER.

34:53.325 --> 34:57.496
- FOREARMS ARE MY THING.

34:57.529 --> 35:00.766
I GET OFF ON PINNING WOMEN'S
ARMS HARD

35:00.799 --> 35:04.570
TILL IT HURTS 'EM.

35:04.603 --> 35:07.139
IT GOT TO THE POINT
WHERE I, YOU KNOW,

35:07.173 --> 35:09.408
PINNED ONE TO THE WALL AND,
BAM,

35:09.441 --> 35:11.577
SNAPPED THAT
LIKE A CHICKEN WING.

35:11.610 --> 35:14.846
- IN OUR ONE-ON-ONE
THIS MORNING,

35:14.880 --> 35:20.286
WE TRACED ELLIOT'S BEHAVIOR
BACK TO HIS FATHER.

35:20.319 --> 35:24.323
- THAT SON OF A BITCH PRETTY
MUCH BEAT ME UP EVERY DAY.

35:24.356 --> 35:25.457
AND, YOU KNOW,
HOW I KNEW IT WAS COMING

35:25.491 --> 35:27.326
IS HE'D ROLL UP HIS SLEEVES.

35:27.359 --> 35:29.395
AND THEN, BAM.

35:29.428 --> 35:31.297
- ELLIOT UNCONSCIOUSLY DIRECTS
HIS ANGER

35:31.330 --> 35:34.833
AT THAT FIRST IMAGE
OF THE ABUSE.

35:34.866 --> 35:38.237
- LIKE I SAY, YOU KNOW?

35:38.270 --> 35:39.605
FOREARMS ARE MY THING.

35:39.638 --> 35:41.740
- NOW, WE'VE SEEN HOW THESE
MALE-ONLY SESSIONS

35:41.773 --> 35:45.444
CAN BE HELPFUL
IN FATHER RE-FIGURATION.

35:45.477 --> 35:47.813
SO--
- SO, WE, UM--

35:47.846 --> 35:49.881
WE ALL ROLL UP OUR SLEEVES,
RIGHT?

35:49.915 --> 35:51.717
AND WE SHOW ELLIOT
A LITTLE LOVE, RIGHT?

35:51.750 --> 35:53.352
- THAT'S RIGHT.

35:53.385 --> 35:54.920
- COME ON, GUYS.
ROLL UP YOUR SLEEVES.

35:54.953 --> 35:56.455
- GIVE HIM A HUG.
SHAKE HIM BY THE HAND.

35:56.488 --> 35:57.789
DO WHATEVER FEELS NATURAL.

35:57.823 --> 36:00.492
- ALL RIGHT, BROTHER.
- HEY, MAN.

36:00.526 --> 36:02.294
- HEY.

36:02.328 --> 36:03.495
- YOU TOTALLY ZEROED IN
ON MY ARMS LAST NIGHT.

36:03.529 --> 36:05.697
THEY'RE NOT GONNA HURT YOU,
ALL RIGHT?

36:05.731 --> 36:07.433
- YEAH.
ALL RIGHT.

36:07.466 --> 36:08.667
- THANK YOU.
- THANKS.

36:08.700 --> 36:11.670
THANKS, DOC.

36:15.474 --> 36:18.710
WHAT'S YOUR PROBLEM, CLAY?

36:18.744 --> 36:20.879
- I'M NOT BREAKING
THE MODESTY CODE.

36:20.912 --> 36:22.381
- COME ON, CLAY.

36:22.414 --> 36:26.418
HELP A FELLOW ADDICT.

36:35.661 --> 36:38.630
HE NEEDS BOTH ARMS, CLAY.

36:57.616 --> 37:00.852
YOU HAVE A TATTOO.

37:00.886 --> 37:03.489
- IT'S EMBARRASSING.

37:03.522 --> 37:04.423
GONNA HAVE IT LASERED OFF.

37:04.456 --> 37:07.826
- WELL, HEY, MAN,
DOESN'T LOOK THAT BAD.

37:07.859 --> 37:10.596
YEAH. HEY.

37:16.468 --> 37:18.036
- WHAT ARE WE MISSING?

37:18.069 --> 37:20.506
EVERY MALE PATIENT
WAS IN THAT ROOM.

37:20.539 --> 37:22.541
- ONE OF THE FEMALES MAYBE?

37:22.574 --> 37:24.943
- NO, THERE'S NO TRANSGENDERS
IN THIS GROUP.

37:24.976 --> 37:27.513
I MEAN, AN EAVESDROPPER,
ONE OF THE CLEANING STAFF?

37:27.546 --> 37:30.349
- WE CHECKED THE EMPLOYEES
IN UTICA, PHILLY, AND RICHMOND.

37:30.382 --> 37:32.718
THERE'S NO OVERLAP.

37:32.751 --> 37:34.420
- UTICA, PHILLY, RICHMOND.

37:34.453 --> 37:36.455
THAT'S WHERE HE STRUCK?
- YEP.

37:36.488 --> 37:39.691
- WELL, THERE'S AN OVERLAP
IN COMPUTER SYSTEMS.

37:39.725 --> 37:42.661
THOSE THREE REHABS USE
THAT SERVICE.

37:42.694 --> 37:43.962
- "SECURE-FILE.
THE FUTURE OF MEDICINE."

37:43.995 --> 37:45.464
WHAT'S THAT?

37:45.497 --> 37:46.432
- THE THERAPISTS
DICTATE THEIR NOTES

37:46.465 --> 37:48.800
AND THAT COMPANY
STORES THEM ELECTRONICALLY.

37:48.834 --> 37:50.369
BUT IT'S SUPPOSED TO BE SECURE.

37:50.402 --> 37:51.970
- BUT A PERP HACKS
INTO THAT SYSTEM,

37:52.003 --> 37:53.605
HE'D KNOW AS MUCH
AS ANYONE IN THE ROOM.

37:53.639 --> 37:55.707
- EXCEPT HERE.

37:55.741 --> 37:57.443
THEY OFFERED THEIR SERVICES.
WE TURNED THEM DOWN.

37:57.476 --> 37:58.877
- WHY?

37:58.910 --> 37:59.711
- WE DIDN'T NEED THEM.

37:59.745 --> 38:01.447
BRETT KINCAID
DOES TOO GOOD A JOB.

38:01.480 --> 38:03.882
- BRETT THE THERAPIST
DOES YOUR COMPUTERS?

38:07.419 --> 38:09.821
- HE WAS IN THE ROOM...

38:09.855 --> 38:14.793
WHEN I TALKED ABOUT ANN.

38:14.826 --> 38:16.628
- WHERE IS HE?

38:16.662 --> 38:18.730
- LEADING THE WOMEN'S SESSION.

38:18.764 --> 38:20.666
ZOE?

38:20.699 --> 38:21.900
I THOUGHT BRETT
WAS RUNNING THIS.

38:21.933 --> 38:23.502
- NO, HE LEFT.
HE WASN'T FEELING WELL.

38:23.535 --> 38:24.836
- WHERE'S COURTNEY?

38:24.870 --> 38:25.971
- SHE DIDN'T SHOW.

38:26.004 --> 38:27.573
YOU DON'T THINK SHE RELAPSED?

38:27.606 --> 38:29.608
- GIVE ME YOUR PHONE.

38:35.747 --> 38:37.483
COURTNEY, IT'S ELLIOT.
WHERE ARE YOU?

38:37.516 --> 38:40.552
- WHERE DO YOU THINK I AM?

38:40.586 --> 38:42.120
DOWN THE STREET.

38:42.153 --> 38:44.122
I GOT YOUR NOTE
AND I'M HERE WAITING.

38:44.155 --> 38:46.692
- WHERE'S "HERE"?
- MCRYAN'S.

38:46.725 --> 38:48.760
THE COP BAR THAT YOU SUGGESTED.

38:48.794 --> 38:51.730
AND THERE'S NOBODY HERE BUT ME.

38:51.763 --> 38:52.664
- COURTNEY, GET OUT OF THERE.

38:52.698 --> 38:56.402
- [chuckles]
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

38:56.435 --> 38:57.703
- NO, LISTEN TO ME!
GET OUT!

38:57.736 --> 38:59.438
I DIDN'T SEND YOU THERE!

38:59.471 --> 39:02.441
MEET ME AT
ROCKEFELLER CENTER!

39:02.474 --> 39:04.576
- [screams]

39:04.610 --> 39:06.778
- COURTNEY!

39:06.812 --> 39:08.079
- DO YOU KNOW?
WHERE IS SHE?

39:08.113 --> 39:09.548
- ABANDONED COP BAR.

39:09.581 --> 39:15.053
- NO MORE SLUTTY WAYS.

39:15.086 --> 39:18.790
I'M CURING YOU.

39:18.824 --> 39:20.759
MAKING YOU RESPECTABLE.

39:20.792 --> 39:22.428
COME ON.

39:36.041 --> 39:38.477
- GET UP.
GET UP!

39:38.510 --> 39:41.513
- [screams and grunts]

39:47.085 --> 39:49.054
I CURED THEM, CAP.

39:49.087 --> 39:52.691
NOW TELL HIM TO LET ME GO.

39:52.724 --> 39:55.527
- I HOPE THEY LOCK YOU UP
FOR LIFE.

39:55.561 --> 39:57.529
- BRETT KINCAID,
YOU'RE UNDER ARREST

39:57.563 --> 39:59.498
FOR THE RAPES
OF DEBBIE SHIELDS,

39:59.531 --> 40:02.200
HOLLY DIMEO,
AND THE ASSAULT OF ANN JACKSON.

40:02.233 --> 40:04.436
- I KNEW YOU WERE A COP.

40:08.974 --> 40:10.642
- YOU LOOK GOOD.

40:10.676 --> 40:13.211
- THANKS.

40:13.244 --> 40:14.813
BUT HE LOOKS LIKE HELL THOUGH.

40:14.846 --> 40:17.015
CAP?

40:17.048 --> 40:18.517
- OH.

40:18.550 --> 40:19.485
- HOW ARE YOU?

40:19.518 --> 40:21.987
- [sighs]

40:22.020 --> 40:23.489
CLINIC'S EMPTY.

40:23.522 --> 40:25.457
- ALL OF YOUR PATIENTS LEFT?

40:25.491 --> 40:27.793
- MM-HMM.

40:27.826 --> 40:29.661
BECAUSE I LET A COP IN.

40:29.695 --> 40:31.930
- I AM SORRY.

40:31.963 --> 40:35.501
- I THOUGHT YOU HATED MY WORK.

40:35.534 --> 40:37.969
- SOME OF THOSE GUYS
SHOULD BE LOCKED UP,

40:38.003 --> 40:39.237
BUT MOST OF 'EM,
YOU WERE HELPING.

40:39.270 --> 40:41.673
- THANK YOU.

40:45.143 --> 40:48.980
SO...ANN HASN'T
WOKEN UP YET, BUT...

40:51.149 --> 40:54.152
WHEN SHE DOES...

40:57.155 --> 40:59.491
I'LL BE THERE.

